/* ==UserStyle==
@name         All Sites - Snow
@namespace    github.com/yherrero/stylus
@version      2.2.0
@description  Snow theme for all supported websites (Discord, Claude.ai, MTools, Teams, Reddit, GitHub)
@author       yherrero
@license      MIT
==/UserStyle== */
